== Research interests
Applied mathematics: convex analysis, variational problems and optimisation algorithms. 

So far, I have mostly worked on extensions of the optimal transport problem.

== Submitted for publication
C., Peyré, Schmitzer, Vialard,, Unbalanced optimal transport: geometry and Kantorovich formulation, Preprint [https://arxiv.org/abs/1508.05216 (ArXiv link)]

_, Scaling Algorithms for Unbalanced Transport Problems, Preprint [https://arxiv.org/abs/1607.05816 (ArXiv link)]

== Publications

C., Peyré, Schmitzer, Vialard, An Interpolating Distance Between Optimal Transport and Fisher–Rao Metrics, Found Comput Math (2016). 
